source: TEXT_DUNGEONOMEGA2_00000_OMEGA_000_000<tab>The power was mine... I obtained the unmeasurable, and now my end is come.
target:
TEXT_DUNGEONOMEGA2_00000_OMEGA_000_000<tab>未知なる力を  得ることができたのに――
ここで終わり――なのですね――

source: TEXT_DUNGEONOMEGA2_00000_OMEGA_000_002<tab>Not an end, you say? We continue onwards...together?
target:
TEXT_DUNGEONOMEGA2_00000_OMEGA_000_002<tab>まだ終わりではないと……
ともに行こうというのですか？

TEXT_DUNGEONOMEGA2_00000_OMEGA_000_003<tab>ガガ……了解……
今回は  アナタの提案を採用しましょう

source: TEXT_DUNGEONOMEGA2_00000_OMEGA_000_004<tab>Your contribution to my experiment is appreciated. Without your unrelenting strength, I would never have realized this new potential.
target:
TEXT_DUNGEONOMEGA2_00000_OMEGA_000_004<tab>検証への協力に感謝します
アナタがたの全力が  ワタシに新たな可能性を与えました

source: TEXT_DUNGEONOMEGA2_00000_OMEGA_000_005<tab>I will embark on a journey, observing and recording all that I encounter. Farewell, mortals. This world has much to teach me...
target:
TEXT_DUNGEONOMEGA2_00000_OMEGA_000_005<tab>ワタシはこの世界を学び  記録する
そのために……  いってきます
